channel.description: Deeper Sounds of Nairobi is a dose of House music.Featuring guest DJs, Artists and Producers from Africa. Deeper Sounds of Nairobi is a promotional radio show recorded and produced in various corners of the world. These two shows are committed to showcasing musical talent coming out of Africa in the House/Dance Genre.

item.content:encoded: Having always been fascinated by the serenity of the ocean coupled with that warm,salty breeze every time you hit the beach,this set was one I had a really great time compiling. I see a large bonfire,dancers on the African sands getting into the groove of things as the evening breeze gently creeps in. The full moon overhead seems to be chasing away the sun as the magnificent golden ball elegantly disappears into the horizon. Energies are steadily intensifying now ,drum tempo is rising,the mood changes from gentle to more rigorous,people are breaking a sweat.
